				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Now I want a SCP-based MTG block.</p> </blockquote> <p>Incidentally, others have made some (fanwork) cards: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-546205/scp-magic-cards">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-546205/scp-magic-cards</a></p> 
				 	]]>
